               <n2016:NUTS CODE="UKH2"/>
               <SHORT_DESCR>
                  <P>Academies included in this Tender:</P>
                  <P>— The Bushey Academy</P>
                  <P>020 8950 9502 London Road Bushey</P>
                  <P>Hertfordshire WD23 3AA.</P>
                  <P>The Harefield Academy.</P>
                  <P>01895 822108 Northwood Way</P>
                  <P>Harefield.</P>
                  <P>Uxbridge.</P>
                  <P>Middlesex.</P>
                  <P>UB9 6ET.</P>
                  <P>Global Academy.</P>
                  <P>0203 019 9000</P>
                  <P>The Old Vinyl Factory.</P>
                  <P>1 Record Walk</P>
                  <P>Hayes.</P>
                  <P>Middlesex.</P>
                  <P>UB3 1DH.</P>
                  <P>— The Bushey Academy:</P>
                  <P>The academy buildings are set in extensive grounds and consist of the new build and 2 period halls, which are adjacent to the main building. All internal areas are fully accessible. The site is easily accessed by road, there is ample on site car parking and it is located within easy reach of the M25 and M1 motorways. In addition to normal education provision, the academy facilities are hired out to individuals and local community groups and is occupied by hirers in the evenings and throughout all holiday periods.</P>
                  <P>Academy roll currently 1200 (age 11-18) rising to a maximum capacity of 1350 (by 9.2019).</P>
                  <P>Academy m2 13 150.</P>
                  <P>— The Harefield Academy:</P>
                  <P>The Harefield Academy is situated in the village of Harefield a historic village in a rural setting in the West London Borough of Hillingdon. Situated on a hill, Harefield is just inside the M25 Motorway. As well as day students, the academy also has onsite boarding provision. The Academy has capacity for 950 Students and 48 Boarders.</P>
                  <P>Academy roll 11 to 16 568 (current).</P>
                  <P>Sixth Form 130 (current).</P>
                  <P>Boarders 36 (current).</P>
                  <P>Academy m2 Approximate area to be cleaned main site 10 000.</P>
                  <P>Approximate area to be cleaned Boarding House 1 650.</P>
                  <P>— Global Academy (UTC).</P>
                  <P>In 9.2016 the Global Academy opened on the iconic Old Vinyl Factory site in Hayes, a UTC specialising in broadcast and digital media alongside a mainstream curriculum of GCSEs and A-Levels.</P>
                  <P>Approximate areas to be cleaned per floor:</P>
